The '''Chandrilan Academy of Sciences''' was a [[school]] in the city of [[Emita/Legends|Emita]] on [[Chandrila/Legends|Chandrila]] for [[Scientist/Legends|scientists]].<ref name="air">''[[Alliance Intelligence Reports]]''</ref> The [[Shi'ido]] [[Mammon Hoole]] and [[Borborygmus Gog]] both studied at this [[academy]]. [[Nashiak Llalik]] finished first in his class here by the time he obtained his degree.<ref name="air" />

